{"url":"/docs/theming/","title":"Theming","description":"CSS variables, dark mode, and customization","plain_text":"Theming chirp-ui uses prefers-color-scheme for dark mode. Override any --chirpui-* variable to customize. Base Variables :root { --chirpui-accent: #7c3aed; --chirpui-container-max: 80rem; } Base colors drive derived states (hover, active, light, muted) via color-mix(). Manual Light/Dark Toggle Set data-theme=&quot;light&quot; or data-theme=&quot;dark&quot; on &lt;html&gt;. Optional Themes &lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;/static/themes/holy-light.css&quot;&gt; Motion All animations respect prefers-reduced-motion. No configuration needed.","excerpt":"Theming chirp-ui uses prefers-color-scheme for dark mode. Override any --chirpui-* variable to customize. Base Variables :root { --chirpui-accent: #7c3aed; --chirpui-container-max: 80rem; } Base...","metadata":{"keywords":["chirp-ui","theming","css","dark mode","variables"],"title":"Theming","type":"doc","weight":30.0,"draft":false,"lang":"en","category":"theming","description":"CSS variables, dark mode, and customization"},"section":"theming","word_count":55,"reading_time":1,"graph":{"nodes":[{"id":"-6806459092770732624","label":"Theming","url":"/docs/theming/","type":"hub","tags":[],"incoming_refs":11,"outgoing_refs":0,"connectivity":11,"reading_time":1,"size":25,"color":"var(--graph-node-hub)","isCurrent":true},{"id":"5234150139125295975","label":"icons","url":"/api/icons/","type":"regular","tags":[],"incoming_refs":0,"outgoing_refs":9,"connectivity":9,"reading_time":1,"size":22,"color":"var(--graph-node-regular)"},{"id":"-1304027309360348006","label":"chirp_ui","url":"/api/chirp_ui/","type":"regular","tags":[],"incoming_refs":0,"outgoing_refs":9,"connectivity":9,"reading_time":1,"size":22,"color":"var(--graph-node-regular)"},{"id":"6883038275937995961","label":"filters","url":"/api/filters/","type":"regular","tags":[],"incoming_refs":0,"outgoing_refs":9,"connectivity":9,"reading_time":1,"s